thread.title: Michael Rutkowski

author: Michael Rutkowski
title: Michael Rutkowski
text:
As far as RTA cabinets go, this is my favorite system so far. I like the metal snap-ins, and the slots were pretty accurate. Much better than any system I have used from other online retailers. Not perfect, but for a rental, you can't beat this price and style of cabinet.
The company was really good with customer service. My first order had a cabinet face which was split, and they replaced it in a very timely manner. Second order, I had to switch up, and it was so easy to do, I wasn't sure they actually took care of it. But it arrived in a few days, and was correct.
